title: Thrash Metal music videos
description:
I have createds this just for fun, and now I thought it would be a good idea to share. Contains some materials from Annihilator, Anthrax, Destruction, Death Angel, Coroner, Forbidden, Voivod, Slayer, Sodom, Kreator, Slayer, Megadeth, Metallica and whose I forgot to mention. Maybe not their best songs or clips, but I don't care. If you have any suggestions, let me know.

Thrash till death!

Ps.: I do not own any rights of these materials. When there is any copyright issues, let me know it too, and I try to solve it
